text: Sybaguasu thoracicum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Olivier in 1795. It is known from Brazil and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Sybaguasu thoracicum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1795
